      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "aComponent",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The component you wish to open. Your application obtains this identifier from the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1516552-findnextcomponent"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " function. If your application registers a component, it can also obtain a component identifier from the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "RegisterComponent"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " function or the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "RegisterComponentResource"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " function. "
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A component instance which identifies your applicationâ€™s connection to the component. You must supply this component instance whenever you call the functions provided by the component. When you close the component, you must also supply this component instance to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1516436-closecomponent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " function."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If it cannot open the specified component, the function returns "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NULL"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "See the description of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "ComponentInstance"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " data type."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Your application must open a component before it can call any component functions. To use this function, you must already have obtained a component identifier. Alternatively, you can use the  "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1516523-opendefaultcomponent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "  function to open a component without calling "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "FindNextComponent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Note that your application may maintain several connections to a single component, or it may have connections to several components at the same time. "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
